Name: I MAED A GAM3 W1TH Z0MBIES 1N IT!!!1
Overview: I MAED A GAM3 W1TH Z0MBIES 1N IT!!!1 is a twin stick shooter designed by Ska Studios' James Silva and released on Xbox Live's Indie Games channel. The game is set to a roughly 13 minute song that shares the game's title. As the song plays out the environment and enemy waves the player faces will change along with it. The goal is to get as a high a score as possible before the song, and the game, ends.
